# Banking Regulatory Reporting Data Platform (GCP)

## Architecture
- GCS (Raw Layer)
- BigQuery (Bronze, Silver, Gold)
- Cloud Composer (Airflow)
- Terraform (IaC)

## Dataset
Czech Financial Dataset (Kaggle)

## Key Features
- Medallion Architecture
- External Table → Raw Table ingestion
- Partitioned BigQuery tables
- Data Quality Checks
- Regulatory reporting layer

## Pipeline Flow
1. Data ingestion → GCS
2. External table validation
3. Bronze load
4. Silver transformation
5. Gold reporting

## Tech Stack
- GCP (BigQuery, GCS, Composer)
- Terraform
- SQL
- Python (Airflow)

## How to Run
1. Terraform apply
2. Upload data to GCS
3. Trigger Airflow DAG
